snippet.title: Jupiter Moons: Mecha - NEW demo gameplay
snippet.description:
A portion of fresh gameplay from NEW demo Jupiter Moons: Mecha
Wishlist ➡ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288540/Jupiter_Moons_Mecha?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=gameplay

Choose your mech, customize your loadout, and build your perfect deck. Experiment with cards to find powerful combinations as you enjoy the tactical combat and deckbuilding in this roguelike adventure!

If you want to learn more, check:

* Discord - https://discord.gg/sHNysXG
* Twitter - https://twitter.com/RockAndBushes
* Reddit - https://www.reddit.com/r/RockAndBushes/
* Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/RockAndBushes/

* Site & Newsletter - https://jupitermoons.org/
